This is a mirror of http://www.vim.org/scripts/script.php?script_id=4520

A simple, easy-to-use Vim alignment plugin

Project home (latest version):
https://github.com/junegunn/vim-easy-align

Demo:
https://raw.github.com/junegunn/vim-easy-align/gif/vim-easy-align.gif

Features:
- Makes the common case easy
  - Comes with a predefined set of alignment rules
  - Provides a fast and intuitive interface
- Extensible
  - You can define your own rules
  - Supports arbitrary regular expressions
- Optimized for code editing
  - Takes advantage of syntax highlighting feature to avoid unwanted alignments
